OL,3,CCharity match in honour of boxer
OL,4,Cdenied title fight for not being white
OL,5,Creturns
OL,7,FA popular fundraiser football match is
OL,8,Freturning to FC United's Broadhurst
OL,9,FPark this year after taking a year out.
OL,11,FThe Len Johnson Charity Match will be
OL,12,Fheld this year on Sunday 12th July for
OL,13,Fits third edition and will once again
OL,14,Fpit the team of FC United legends
OL,15,Fagainst a team of TV personalities,
OL,16,Fmusicians, actors, footballers and
OL,17,FYouTube creators dubbed the Len
OL,18,FJohnson Allstars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
