OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781100698
OL,3,CCharity match in honour of boxer
OL,4,Cdenied title fight for not being white
OL,5,Creturns
OL,7,FThe match is to raise funds for a
OL,8,Fpermanent tribute to the 'Uncrowned
OL,9,FChampion' Len Johnson - the Manchester
OL,10,Fboxer who was denied a title shot
OL,11,Fdespite beating around 100 opponents.
OL,13,FThis was due to a colour bar that was
OL,14,Fin place by the British Boxing Board
OL,15,Fof Control who upheld that 'Rule 24'
OL,16,Fstated that in order to fight for a
OL,17,FBritish title, the fighter's parents
OL,18,Fmust both be white.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781100698
OL,3,CCharity match in honour of boxer
OL,4,Cdenied title fight for not being white
OL,5,Creturns
OL,7,FAs well as a boxer, Johnson was also
OL,8,Fan accomplished activist, fighting
OL,9,Fagainst racism and for civil rights,
OL,10,Feven getting the colour bar lifted at
OL,11,Flocal pub The Old Abbey Taphouse after
OL,12,Fa standoff with the landlord who had
OL,13,Fpreviously refused to serve him
OL,14,Fbecause he was black.
OL,16,FJohnson even garnered support from
OL,17,FAmerican singer Paul Robeson and
OL,18,Fattended the 5th Pan African Congress
OL,19,Fin Manchester, further cementing
OL,20,Fhimself in the city's history.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781100698
OL,3,CCharity match in honour of boxer
OL,4,Cdenied title fight for not being white
OL,5,Creturns
OL,7,FDespite this, he was largely forgotten
OL,8,Fwhen he died in 1974 and in 2020 a
OL,9,Fcampaign to build a statue of the
OL,10,FMancunian has been started by local
OL,11,Factivists Deej Malik-Johnson and Lamin
OL,12,FTouray, leading to the first
OL,13,Ffundraiser match in 2023.
OL,15,FLamin said; "I'm delighted the Len
OL,16,FJohnson match is back it's a brilliant
OL,17,Fday out for the community and at a
OL,18,Ftime of increasing division in society
OL,19,Fthis feels like a breath of fresh air.
OL,26,@wD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
