PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781100698
OL,3,CCharity match in honour of boxer
OL,4,Cdenied title fight for not being white
OL,5,Creturns
OL,7,F"Sport brings people together this is
OL,8,Fproudly an anti racist event
OL,9,Fcelebrating local black history but
OL,10,Falso our collective Mancunian history
OL,11,Fwe will continue to celebrate the
OL,12,Fremarkable story of Len Johnson and
OL,13,Fjust like Len we will keep fighting to
OL,14,Freach our #150,00 target for the
OL,15,Fstatue."
OL,17,FThe plan once enough money is raised
OL,18,Fis to have a statue in Manchester City
OL,19,FCentre, with the group actively
OL,20,Fworking with council to establish a
OL,21,Fsuitable location.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@HO]
