OL,3,CCharity match in honour of boxer
OL,4,Cdenied title fight for not being white
OL,5,Creturns
OL,7,FThe match is on Sunday 12th July and
OL,8,Fwill kick off at 3pm.
OL,10,FTo attend or learn more, visit the Len
OL,11,FJohnson Charity Match event page here.
